episodes.title: Caught in Maryland:  Unraveling the Zizian Cult Murders
episodes.description:
Hello everyone! This video is about the Zizian Cult and their apprehension in Frostburg, Maryland. That should be self-explanatory in itself. So, check it out and let me know what you think in the comments below.

If you or a loved one is in a cult and wants help getting out, you should contact cult intervention specialists, such as The Freedom of Mind Resource Center:  https://freedomofmind.com/

Thank you all for watching, and as usual, if you're a fan of urban legends, folklore, unsolved mysteries, cold cases, and all things mysterious, make sure you like and subscribe to the channel.
